Cell[TextData[{
 "At ",
 ButtonBox["TOSSIB",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["https://susinfra.com/tossib"], None},
  ButtonNote->"https://susinfra.com/tossib"],
 " and ",
 ButtonBox["SASSI",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["https://susinfra.com/sassi"], None},
  ButtonNote->"https://susinfra.com/sassi"],
 " we worked to understand how UN SDG are linked together to understand how \
investment in one of them can improve other goals. Students from the \
2021/2022 cohorts have done their thesis in this topic. Very interesting to \
see how the network analysis of the interlinkage structure of SDGs provides \
information about the social economic state of a nation (unsupervised \
learning)."
}], "Subitem",
