d8d19c34ac52"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "After Copernicus, Kepler and Galileo, it became accepted that the Earth was \
revolving around the Sun. The whole European society needed to be reeducated \
to accept this now demonstrated natural phenomenon, including the Roman \
Catholic Church. This was at the time a tremendous government and religion ",
 StyleBox["actionable insight!",
  FontColor->RGBColor[1, 0, 0]]
}], "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.812176561061619*^9, 
  3.812176779700358*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"cc337eb4-907d-4770-9383-\
5dc74eb1831d"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
Related to Covid, there are innumerous examples of how data science provokes \
actionable insights, not always they are for the benefit of the society. \
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.812176561061619*^9, 3.81217675688402*^9}, {
  3.812176792575093*^9, 3.812176836005505*^9}, {3.977292444506591*^9, 
  3.977292448474249*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"fcd5b419-d480-4c3a-b323-\
708be38ff738"],

