  3.812176792575093*^9, 3.812176847624695*^9}, {3.812176947860715*^9, 
  3.812177018844493*^9}, {3.8121772545908747`*^9, 
  3.8121772545990467`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f0d5e97b-fa8a-4da0-b70b-\
3c9a1d8e03fc"],

Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["A paper in The Lancet was retracted [",
  FontSize->16],
 StyleBox[ButtonBox["The Guardian",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2020/jun/05/lancet-had-to-\
do-one-of-the-biggest-retractions-in-modern-history-how-could-this-happen"], 
    None},
  ButtonNote->
   "https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2020/jun/05/lancet-had-to-do-\
one-of-the-biggest-retractions-in-modern-history-how-could-this-happen"],
  FontSize->16],
 StyleBox["]. It was about the effect of Covid patients receiving \
hydroxychloroquine leading to heartbeat irregularities, and that halted drug \
tests across the world. The data used had an unreliable source, of a company \
that has emerged out of nowhere and was claiming to have clinical data from \
several hospital around the word [",
  FontSize->16],
 StyleBox[ButtonBox["The Guardian",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/jun/04/unreliable-data-doubt-\
snowballed-covid-19-drug-research-surgisphere-coronavirus-hydroxychloroquine"]\
, None},
  ButtonNote->
   "https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/jun/04/unreliable-data-doubt-\
snowballed-covid-19-drug-research-surgisphere-coronavirus-hydroxychloroquine"],
  FontSize->16],
 StyleBox["]. The company has still not explained the source of the data. \
[read ",
  FontSize->16],
 StyleBox[ButtonBox["Blog by Derek owe",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    URL["https://blogs.sciencemag.org/pipeline/archives/2020/06/02/\
surgisphere-and-their-data"], None},
  ButtonNote->
   "https://blogs.sciencemag.org/pipeline/archives/2020/06/02/surgisphere-and-\
their-data"],
  FontSize->16],
 StyleBox["]. ",
  FontSize->16]
}], "Subsubitem",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.812176561061619*^9, 3.81217675688402*^9}, {
  3.812176792575093*^9, 3.812176847624695*^9}, {3.812176947860715*^9, 
